4671b885-d603-4946-af70-40950d4e5650.Text: Lord Cap'n, the enforces have reported an incursion within the ship by nefarious forces and the auger crews have spotted hostile ships lurking at the edge of the system. What are your orders?

18ed6a24-53ea-4bb7-b1f7-51c36dfcb914.Text: My retinue is restless. Inform Sauerback that I shall deal with the situation aboard the ship personally.

38e0b0cc-45b4-4de0-a964-42dc92c2af28.Text: "Lord Cap'n." {n}Ravor acknowledges you with a nod and turns away.{/n}

414506b3-ae82-4ba7-854d-d270ca79b68b.Text: The crew has grown sluggish. Master Helmsman, set a course to intercept those voidships at once!.
